# Code for the paper "A data-driven robust approach to a problem of optimal replacement in maintenance"

This repository contains the scripts used to generate the experiments in this paper.

## Files
- `RP1_Exp1_mixtureData_alpha.py` — Experiment 1 (varying alpha / plots)
- `RP1_Exp1_mixtureData_withPolicy.py` — Experiment 1 (policy printouts / plots)
- `RP1_Exp2_mixtureData_R.py` — Experiment 2 (varying R)
- `RP1_Exp3_mixtureData_Pi.py` — Experiment 3 (varying mixture probability)

## How to run
Run any script with Python 3, e.g.
```bash
python RP1_Exp2_mixtureData_R.py

